{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm leans across the table and whispers.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MALCOLM
{DIALOGUE}: Cole...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cole looks at Malcolm.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MALCOLM
{DIALOGUE}: One day...
{META_DATA}: (beat)
{DIALOGUE}: You're going to sound just like them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Beat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cole's chin starts to tremble.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His voice cracks.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COLE
{META_DATA}: (whispers)
{DIALOGUE}: Promise?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Beat.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MALCOLM
{META_DATA}: (whispers)
{DIALOGUE}: Promise.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm and Cole sit in silence and listen to THE SOUND OF CHILDREN PLAYING.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HALLWAY - EVENING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm sorts through the many bills on the mail table.
