{DIALOGUE}: "Zoloft Anti-depressant" "To be taken twice daily"
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm gently puts down the plastic bottle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He gazes at the still figure of his wife as the water covers her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm leaves the bathroom.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He makes sure not to make a noise with the door as he closes it shut.
{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. DARREN'S HOUSE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Colorful balloons flutter in the wind in front of an old grey stone home.
