{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She looks to Lynn.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She turns around with Cole in her arms.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LYNN
{META_DATA}: (desperate whispers)
{DIALOGUE}: Help me get him in the car.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HOSPITAL RECEPTION AREA - AFTERNOON
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Colorful murals don the curved walls of the pediatric reception area.
