{DIALOGUE}: What's wrong with Cole?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Beat.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DR. HILL
{DIALOGUE}: The tests indicate he did not have a seizure.
{DIALOGUE}: In fact he's doing fine.
{DIALOGUE}: After some rest, he could go home tonight.
