{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mr. Cunningham smiles.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MR. CUNNINGHAM
{DIALOGUE}: You're welcome, Cole.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They share a look before walking out of the prop room and entering the hall.
