{DIALOGUE}: They rebuilt the whole thing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Beat.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COLE
{DIALOGUE}: I know.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SCHOOL - AFTERNOON
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It begins to rain.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm pulls his jacket over his head as he scurries up the stairs of the school.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HALL - AFTERNOON
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm stands and catches his breath in the corridor of St. Anthony's Academy.
