{CHARACTER_NAME}: COLE
{META_DATA}: (soft)
{DIALOGUE}: See you tomorrow.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Malcolm's face shows his losing battle against his emotions.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He doesn't turn to look back.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. CAR - LATE AFTERNOON
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A rain-soaked bridge.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A two-lane road merges to one lane around a severe car accident.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A rear-ended car has jumped the sidewalk and hit the guard rail of the bridge.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The driver is helped out by police.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He's shaken but okay.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Police flares guide the cars as they crawl by.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lynn and Cole are standing still in bumper-to-bumper traffic.
